'''雨淞'''(Glaze<ref>{{cite book|title=International Cloud Atlas|year=1975|publisher=Secretariat of the World Meteorological Organization|location=Geneva|ISBN=92-63-10407-7|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/manualonobservat00worl}}</ref>,glaze ice,glazed frost)，是冰凍的雨或毛毛雨撞擊表面時產生的光滑，透明且均勻的冰層。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://weather.about.com/od/g/g/glaze.htm|title=Glaze Ice definition|last=Oblack|first=Rachelle|accessdate=2009-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080822014756/http://weather.about.com/od/g/g/glaze.htm|archive-date=2008-08-22|url-status=dead}}</ref>它的外觀類似於清除由[[過冷|過冷]][[水滴|水滴]]形成的冰。在冬季的[[溫帶氣候|溫帶氣候]]中，當高空中的[[降水|降水]]形成並在[[地表|地表]]降到低於[[冰點|冰點]]的溫度時，這是一種相對普遍的現象。

